# Added by cargo

/target

# Mise lockfile — untracked while Renovate's mise artifact updater runs `mise lock` without setting
# `MISE_TRUSTED_CONFIG_PATHS` or `MISE_LOCKED`, which makes every Renovate dep PR fail the artifact step
# with "Config files ... are not trusted". Mend hosted Renovate exposes no way to inject those env vars
# from the user side, so the project-side workaround is to stop tracking the lockfile. Re-track (and drop
# this entry) once that upstream behaviour changes.
mise.lock
